description: Lists all the analysis reports created for the DB instance. The reports are sorted based on the start time of each report.

parameters.name: ServiceType
parameters.description: The Amazon Web Services service for which Performance Insights returns metrics. Valid value is RDS.

parameters.name: Identifier
parameters.description: An immutable identifier for a data source that is unique for an Amazon Web Services Region. Performance Insights gathers metrics from this data source. In the console, the identifier is shown as ResourceID. When you call DescribeDBInstances, the identifier is returned as DbiResourceId. To use a DB instance as a data source, specify its DbiResourceId value. For example, specify db-ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTU1VW2X.

nested_items.name: AnalysisReports
nested_items.description: List of reports including the report identifier, start and end time, creation time, and status.

nested_items.name: AnalysisReportId
nested_items.description: The name of the analysis report.

nested_items.name: CreateTime
nested_items.description: The time you created the analysis report.

nested_items.name: StartTime
nested_items.description: The start time of the analysis in the report.

nested_items.name: EndTime
nested_items.description: The end time of the analysis in the report.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The status of the analysis report.

nested_items.name: Tags
nested_items.description: List of all the tags added to the analysis report.

nested_items.name: Key
nested_items.description: A key is the required name of the tag. The string value can be from 1 to 128 Unicode characters in length and can't be prefixed with aws: or rds:. The string can only contain only the set of Unicode letters, digits, white-space, --_', --.', --:', --/', --=', --+', ---', --@' (Java regex: "^([\\p{L}\\p{Z}\\p{N}_.:/=+\\-@]*)$").

nested_items.name: Value
nested_items.description: A value is the optional value of the tag. The string value can be from 1 to 256 Unicode characters in length and can't be prefixed with aws: or rds:. The string can only contain only the set of Unicode letters, digits, white-space, --_', --.', --:', --/', --=', --+', ---', --@' (Java regex: '^([\p{L}\p{Z}\p{N}_.:/=+\-@]*)$').

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: An optional pagination token provided by a previous request. If this parameter is specified, the response includes only records beyond the token, up to the value specified by MaxResults.
